U/ipBAMjwBiZYA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipBAMjwBiZYA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;人工智能的繁荣带动了台湾股市的飙升，全球最先进芯片的大部分都是由台湾生产的。该岛的交易所目前是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/CHUyYgAjIXzoQ-w9qytqBXOeUVOUIYs58vr5n9_mmIZdJww-R4TfYnV8G_DzViAIkvZCU5UgmILFBbprrhz4n5iYaGZ1F-i8-8ZpO_OB_hkuKMivTh3JrCiEX7ymb3dZ_IQh9Ge21a9jPgxalYZyZIeXAX9wMl0HhkrEQl1xp34lxfjnTlvMYpMOl8gO9KTQeWXZ6z9UAixfzAggff4mIm2FLnW7JzqWl5YsigFTGrPgJJhiEQ1F_f3rKP0Y6rbgg6wMMqKFh1aZVsp6HZOarYKB7wfgVlZmWRiWofgkEd0FbYfx2XJ7MRHPtsihnSHNt6sNAQZBVnTXwaqUY04genlScav6_9N6ljjJxNUStiyqxgMvzd2_vECHs6Z26ng4LImcsTSWUPIlfwc7r6N0siZTQyn3klPCG5SS5rfjB8DgcwmFZtfFxPocsVLz3OZtXx6A5rBNr572g6XGgPXT9zyiM6grEJ1dpJMDKECV95RZl6Gtmt-gyaafRqZh3yN8AJLZeC7jg_avcwQgJ9edgLxEiCCobnAoGK7CxEpsfCDv/1Z9TT_wsw-jJVx-1ycqbMX8nx3xx0nmf/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="台湾超越印度成为全球第五大股市"&gt;世界第五大交易所&lt;/a&gt;，超过了印度，后者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/4Zi7VbPcwE3o5razIi3OsxzQtNm7LAsjN_7nLbwZRk8nK8zyhzj6s0LgQwuu_h-s8w1PGKrjVi9aguuHZoilT8teOadq2oFFN5tw0lma-5vWLujpy8MqM2WUBh9ptp7A73oRU4b78DfMhmZZoLnKZQw45osJgl4M6eOAagEmZGdWBSgxZmkgRG-hlk3oiLjrRD5qUNurmvEtEuKlYIsChSEp_01nE-TRhISTmDSb17RskXrPRxf_WWp31QwBa_OCCt5xM992q5fbqr8FMV-xpk2sozZJkbgv7TeCK9_W0QpGzVjnHKaTxMlo7M2C3bFfEsGlCcoUc6bZnYElYg3BmdDfGZ_uVMuH1Ol9V1xOr1KykZYDbdE_XHuY2rVGaCe3K_v8xbGUVrFvmDkdijRGArBzn_UOIhZyHFjiaHTVCIXGqsnmqlcd6Qklr5eDB6mxwZMC1boelr1X52M_0WXF8RM1nWNYk3tuD-E64LcpHwJi0kOZzXhXWBdbM6BkbM7GWgPTQeY6z39G6JwmD9hAdQVlzXyM859t4Tqqs1wZuS8/xjnfymtasmKtwackutmOrErpu9etuYFS/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="印度的炎热夜晚给电网带来压力并威胁健康"&gt;正面临能源成本飙升&lt;/a&gt;、企业盈利增长放缓以及缺乏与人工智能建设直接相关的公司的问题。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;近三十年来，谈论新西兰的房地产价值——房地产价值不断上涨，让很大一部分人过上富裕的生活——成为了全国性的消遣。如今，随着这个见证了世界上最大的房地产繁荣之一的国家正在与借贷成本上升和移民疲软引发的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/qrNZ9cajKZUy6_gdxlGSc2mMOiTq8u5YWwoWksWseY45QKV_zkgff7sWVvtfEZDpmTo22tOv7QTX7lUxEInk-thK0tMzf5XpLuQxDgy7MyxxpLYc2CzN4Wv2cOFl6luO95a0hbbVLmnFknxK-r5eP6a5UTsStyAfdSBUixqonzjuZ3SmRsJSC_s755SPMmhm-koM-Ak2fQbK33zh6OACvKMjDzDn_-Nv4OjijrUpcpKgyjuRH_zPM-S8Hanux_Z2wEmDsdFQgQd6t_NG6PANjfNy3wg7NTN-6gmzA78tt7WEL5KJwVvsdFkKCf5rkwX7BTHByvSYdDpvls8Z_Gv2eOSS5UrQn9I-_PMutNOb7IStgbworv2sU_3df7WjYk-EWRnVTPDReL8n0J82pyWlc82_maBtad9x9qUnNwVIDTITfxny_RtxxDRO3xK9GJsD1_m1AYkGlxpXnkElf30Z0ZQcAvb6h3V-oSG0fXpPJ4Ts9KvzeaOUc-06WObULKrMo9_LPsjpFj0O82EkGsdRs60SSV2nA0MSun03cA6EiMfR70Kv/eqpuD-Q-WJDVU-Mny6J2G3FFoCtFkyjk/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="世界上最极端的房地产繁荣正在扰乱整个经济"&gt;长期低迷&lt;/a&gt;作斗争，人们的议论已经变成了哀叹。新西兰的困境说明了世界各国政府面临的困境：如何在不侵蚀财富和不影响经济的情况下让人们更容易拥有住房。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih4Kv2Vh20Lw/v1/-1x-1.jpg" alt="A Freeze The Rent rally at Riverside Church in New York City in May 2025. Photographer: Katie Godowski&amp;amp;#x2F;MediaPunch &amp;amp;#x2F;IPX&amp;amp;#x2F;AP" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2025 年 5 月，纽约市河滨教堂举行的“冻结租金”集会。摄影师：Katie Godowski&amp;amp;#x2F;MediaPunch &amp;amp;#x2F;IPX&amp;amp;#x2F;AP" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih4Kv2Vh20Lw/v1/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display